  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Assessing sleep and circadian health in severely obese adolescents undergoing bariatric&#xD;
      surgery and examine relation to health outcomes including insulin sensitivity and percent&#xD;
      weight loss to date at 1-year and evaluate the impact of sleep extension on health outcomes&#xD;
      in this population.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
